        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Safe Helicopters Now Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax credit equal to 10% of the costs of making changes to a fuel system in an emergency medical rotorcraft to comply with certain requirements for fuel system crash resistance. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
